${misconceptionNote}
${errorNote}
${conceptFocusSection}

ADAPTIVE INSTRUCTION:
${adaptiveInstruction}

${avoidSection}

QUESTION INSTRUCTION:
${bloom.instruction}

Required JSON structure:
